               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> (v. <foreign xml:lang="gez">እራዛ፡</foreign>) <gramGrp> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos> </gramGrp>, nomen avis; fortasse species gallinarum sylvestrium vel agrestium; animalibus gregariis ducem sequentibus adnumerantur <foreign xml:lang="gez">ንህብ፡ ወራዛ፡ ወኰራኪ፡ ወቶራት፡ ወአንስርት፡ ወአልህምተ፡ ገዳም፡ ወዘመደ፡ ዓሣት፡ ዘዘዚአሆሙ፡</foreign> F.N. 44,2. – <lbl expand="Vocabularium Aethiopicum, -a -a">Voc. Ae.</lbl>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ራዛ፡</foreign> (v. <foreign xml:lang="gez">እራዛ፡</foreign>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘ፡ የበዳ፡ ዶሮ፡</foreign> – Isenb. in <lbl expand="lexicon">lex.</lbl> p. 48: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ራዛ፡</foreign> „a large white bird, which eats grass-hoppers“. </sense>
               
